exclusivity agreements credit card brands have with card-payment
processor companies in a bid to foster competition in this
market, Aldo Mendes, the monetary policy director at the bank
said.  Mendes, speaking at an event in  Sao Paulo , said there is
room to lower credit card transaction costs for retailers and
